'''Philip Ray''' (1897-1969) was a British [[film actor|film]] and [[televison actor]].<ref>http://ftvdb.bfi.org.uk/sift/individual/97493</ref>

==Selected filmography==
* ''[[Send for Paul Temple]]'' (1946)
* ''[[No Place for Jennifer]]'' (1950)
* ''[[Derby Day (1952 film)|Derby Day]]'' (1952)
* ''[[The Good Die Young]]'' (1954)
* ''[[A Night to Remember]]'' (1958)
* ''[[Sons and Lovers (1960 film)|Sons and Lovers]]'' (1960)

